  "texts": [
    "Figure 9 depicts results on which devices respondents use and how they rate the overall impact of LLMs on dementia management and care.",
    "In both groups a variety of devices was used, although amongst PwD tablets were more dominant whereas among supporters smartphones were more dominant.",
    "The overall impact of LLMs on dementia care and management was seen more positively by PwD than supporters.",
    "Whereas only 1 respondent in the PwD group indicated \"negative\", 3 supporters indicated the impact as \"very negative\".",
    "Nevertheless, larger proportions in both groups rated the impact as \"positive\" or \"very positive\" (PwD: 9 respondents, supporters: 8)."
  ],
